00:31:58.950 --> 00:32:04.539
I hope that you will enjoy the science that
comes after the myths.

00:32:04.539 --> 00:32:09.070
I hope you'll agree that the truth has a magic
of its own.

00:32:09.070 --> 00:32:12.460
The truth is
more magical in the best and most exciting

00:32:12.460 --> 00:32:18.279
sense of the word than any myth or made up
mystery or miracle.

00:32:18.279 --> 00:32:23.049
Science has its own magic, the magic of reality."

